1.title: Summary
1.content: The WASP2 board is designed to be a general purpose demonstration platform for the Sierra Wireless CF3 format cellular modules. It presents a subset of the CF3 interfaces to the end users via a 30 way (2x15) 0.1” header. Some of the more commonly used interfaces are “level shifted” .

3.title: Host board Compatibility
3.content: PCs with USB 2.0 connectivity . Raspberry Pi 4 Model B Raspberry Pi 3 Model B+ Raspberry Pi 3 Model B Raspberry Pi 2 Model B Raspberry Pi Zero W Raspberry Pi Zero .
